race.comment: MY WARRIOR (7) was a last-start winner from the inside at this track and distance (20.01) after charging straight to the lead, scoring by 5 lengths. Expected to go close again. BOBBY BONUS (2) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing second (17.02) at Casino in a Grade 5 over 300m. Leading chance. SEND A TEXT (1) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only one length (20.46) behind Miss Blue Blaze at this track. Leading chance. WHY A MACIE (3) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.
